===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{botany}} A [[discrete]] unit in the center of a flower which receives the [[pollen]] and produces a [[fruit]], consisting of one or more fused [[carpel|carpels]].  Some plant species have more than one [[pistil]] per flower.

